Read ONLY when about to use the matching tools / receive the matching system messages:
- `.cursor/skills/kc-autopilot/SKILL.md` — user says "start autopilot", or you call `autopilot_*` / receive `[AUTOPILOT_TICK]` `[AUTOPILOT_PAUSED]` `[AUTOPILOT_BUDGET_EXHAUSTED]`.

